Second Department,

June, 1947.

(June 2, 1947.) Theresa B. Frazier et al., Respondents, v. Westchester Street Transportation Company, Inc., Appellant, et al., Defendants.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals granted. Present — Hagarty, Acting P. J,, Carswell, Adel, Nolan and Sneed, JJ. [See ante, p. 819.]
